        <Parent_String>American Scene [300164372], modern North American fine arts styles and movements [300108689], modern North American [300018196], modern American [300018115], The Americas [300016617], styles, periods, and cultures by region [300111079], Styles and Periods (hierarchy name) [300015646], Styles and Periods Facet [300264088]</Parent_String>
